WEBVTT

00:01:47.719 --> 00:01:48.319
Lao Tong

00:01:48.799 --> 00:01:49.760
The boss is looking for you.

00:01:51.159 --> 00:01:51.840
Go on, hurry.

00:02:17.319 --> 00:02:19.319
Brother Tong, what's wrong?

00:02:19.319 --> 00:02:20.680
It's nothing. I got up too fast.

00:02:21.560 --> 00:02:22.639
Have something to eat.

00:02:22.639 --> 00:02:23.280
Okay.

00:02:27.719 --> 00:02:28.599
Branch Manager.

00:02:29.280 --> 00:02:30.080
Tong.

00:02:34.479 --> 00:02:35.560
You wanted to see me?

00:02:37.520 --> 00:02:38.400
Tong.

00:02:39.919 --> 00:02:41.319
You've finally come to your senses.

00:02:42.639 --> 00:02:43.520
Come to your senses.

00:02:46.960 --> 00:02:47.560
Here.

00:02:50.120 --> 00:02:50.919
So?

00:02:51.240 --> 00:02:53.879
You must have closed the deal this time, right?

00:02:55.439 --> 00:02:56.319
Closed it, right?

00:02:58.039 --> 00:02:59.560
I won't ask for the details.

00:03:00.080 --> 00:03:00.919
When the time comes,

00:03:01.759 --> 00:03:03.400
just tell me the result.

00:03:29.159 --> 00:03:29.759
Finish it.

00:03:29.759 --> 00:03:30.919
Alright, alright.

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:33.400
Look who's getting protective now.

00:03:33.400 --> 00:03:35.000
He hasn't even drunk half of it.

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:35.599
Enough.

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:37.840
He's had too much.

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:39.039
Here, sober up.

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:43.879
Getting protective.

00:03:49.240 --> 00:03:50.719
So sweet, are we?

00:03:55.360 --> 00:03:56.560
Got it, got it.

00:03:58.240 --> 00:03:59.080
Out.

00:04:01.439 --> 00:04:02.719
Xiao Jia, you come here.

00:04:12.960 --> 00:04:14.120
Are you okay, Lao Tong?

00:04:15.520 --> 00:04:16.240
Lao Tong.

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:18.160
Are you okay?

00:04:18.160 --> 00:04:20.120
I'm fine, I'm fine, I'm fine.

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:42.439
Honey.

00:04:42.800 --> 00:04:45.439
This promotion is probably out of reach again.

00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:48.199
The next promotion likely won't happen either.

00:04:48.560 --> 00:04:49.560
I'm sorry.

00:04:49.639 --> 00:04:51.000
What a mess this is.

00:04:56.199 --> 00:04:57.000
Brother Tong.

00:05:09.319 --> 00:05:10.000
Manager Li.

00:05:15.519 --> 00:05:16.639
What are you doing here?

00:05:17.240 --> 00:05:18.160
Just looking around.

00:05:19.959 --> 00:05:23.000
Tom, are you doing okay working here?

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:25.639
How many times have I told you?

00:05:25.759 --> 00:05:27.839
My surname is Li, not Tang.

00:05:28.439 --> 00:05:29.000
No.

00:05:29.360 --> 00:05:31.079
Is this a place for you to just look around?

00:05:31.480 --> 00:05:33.439
This is our office area.

00:05:33.720 --> 00:05:35.920
What are you, a foreigner, looking at?

00:05:36.079 --> 00:05:38.519
Go on, get out, out, out.

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:42.519
Lianbao, what are you doing? Let go.

00:05:42.600 --> 00:05:43.279
This foreigner...

00:05:43.279 --> 00:05:44.680
was wandering around our office area. I...

00:05:44.680 --> 00:05:45.720
What nonsense are you pulling?

00:05:46.560 --> 00:05:48.519
This is the representative from our new investor.

00:05:48.519 --> 00:05:49.279
Kevin.

00:05:50.879 --> 00:05:52.800
Kevin, I'm so sorry.

00:05:52.800 --> 00:05:54.759
Why didn't you let us know you were coming?

00:05:54.759 --> 00:05:56.240
So we could have prepared to host you.

00:05:56.399 --> 00:05:56.879
Right.

00:05:56.879 --> 00:05:59.759
I prefer to assess investment targets with my own eyes.

00:06:00.319 --> 00:06:01.199
Understood, understood.

00:06:01.519 --> 00:06:03.199
In our words, it's an incognito inspection.

00:06:03.439 --> 00:06:04.439
Yes, yes, yes.

00:06:05.160 --> 00:06:06.560
You invested in our company?

00:06:07.079 --> 00:06:08.480
Then why didn't you tell me?

00:06:08.480 --> 00:06:09.839
What's going on with you?

00:06:10.040 --> 00:06:12.279
Does Kevin need to report his investments to you?

00:06:12.279 --> 00:06:13.319
It's fine, it's fine.

00:06:13.319 --> 00:06:16.399
Tom and I have a special relationship.

00:06:19.399 --> 00:06:21.399
My wife is his ex-wife.

00:06:21.959 --> 00:06:24.240
And he is my daughter's biological father.

00:06:29.079 --> 00:06:30.920
Lianbao, you're divorced?

00:06:31.720 --> 00:06:33.439
Last time we had dinner,

00:06:33.439 --> 00:06:34.879
you said your wife found a...

00:06:34.879 --> 00:06:36.759
particularly unreliable loser.

00:06:37.160 --> 00:06:38.399
Excuse me, everyone.

00:06:38.399 --> 00:06:41.279
I need to speak with Tom privately.

00:06:42.399 --> 00:06:43.040
Tom.

00:06:45.319 --> 00:06:48.439
Yuanyuan came back from your place with a fever last time.

00:06:49.040 --> 00:06:50.839
Please, when you take her out in the future,

00:06:50.839 --> 00:06:52.360
make sure to take proper precautions.

00:06:52.519 --> 00:06:53.240
Is it serious?

00:06:54.160 --> 00:06:55.399
Nana is taking care of her.

00:06:55.519 --> 00:06:56.920
It shouldn't be a big problem.

00:06:57.920 --> 00:06:58.879
Alright, everyone.

00:06:58.879 --> 00:07:01.079
Please, show me around.

00:07:01.079 --> 00:07:02.399
The honor is ours. Please.

00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:05.040
Lianbao, Lianbao.

00:07:27.439 --> 00:07:28.279
What?

00:07:29.279 --> 00:07:32.240
Is Yuanyuan feeling better now?

00:07:32.480 --> 00:07:34.959
Just took medicine, she's asleep.

00:07:35.560 --> 00:07:37.720
Then let me see her.

00:07:39.879 --> 00:07:42.040
Just one look, one look, is that too much?

00:07:42.040 --> 00:07:44.040
What were you doing before the divorce?

00:07:44.560 --> 00:07:45.839
How many times?

00:07:46.079 --> 00:07:47.040
Jenny was sick,

00:07:47.040 --> 00:07:49.040
and you were still out drinking and socializing.

00:07:49.160 --> 00:07:50.879
Now you want to be a good father?

00:07:51.160 --> 00:07:52.439
I'm telling you, it's too late.

00:07:56.800 --> 00:07:57.519
Wait a second.

00:07:58.040 --> 00:07:58.800
What?

00:07:59.319 --> 00:08:00.759
Move the camera back a bit.

00:08:02.279 --> 00:08:04.160
Yes, yes, there, stop.

00:08:10.040 --> 00:08:11.040
What's wrong with you?

00:08:11.439 --> 00:08:12.680
That doll, I asked someone

00:08:12.680 --> 00:08:14.040
and finally managed to buy it.

00:08:14.199 --> 00:08:15.439
Yuanyuan loved it so much.

00:08:15.439 --> 00:08:17.079
How could you just toss it aside?

00:08:18.160 --> 00:08:19.199
This one?

00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:20.600
Here.

00:08:23.319 --> 00:08:25.079
This whole wall of dolls,

00:08:25.079 --> 00:08:25.800
they're all from Kevin.

00:08:25.800 --> 00:08:28.040
He brought them back from abroad for Jenny.

00:08:28.040 --> 00:08:29.480
And they're limited editions.

00:09:27.840 --> 00:09:29.159
I just had a dream.

00:09:34.440 --> 00:09:36.360
Couldn't get back to sleep, so I came up to sit for a while.

00:09:47.879 --> 00:09:49.720
Auntie used to live in my room.

00:09:52.039 --> 00:09:54.120
I lived with Grandma and Grandpa in your courtyard.

00:09:57.080 --> 00:09:58.799
When we were kids, every year at this time,

00:09:59.960 --> 00:10:01.679
Auntie would give me thirty cents a day

00:10:01.679 --> 00:10:03.320
to buy chilled soda.

00:10:05.639 --> 00:10:07.600
I wouldn't share with Lianbao or Qiu'er.

00:10:11.320 --> 00:10:13.080
The soda was just for the two of us.

00:10:20.320 --> 00:10:21.960
I just dreamed of Auntie.

00:10:22.320 --> 00:10:23.480
She gave me thirty cents again,

00:10:23.480 --> 00:10:24.799
telling me to buy soda.

00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:01.799
Manager Li.

00:11:01.799 --> 00:11:04.000
As soon as Kevin arrived, he wants to push cost reduction and efficiency improvement.

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:05.639
He wants to cut all inefficient positions.

00:11:05.799 --> 00:11:07.399
Now the whole company is in a panic.

00:11:07.399 --> 00:11:09.200
Everyone's waiting for you to take charge.

00:11:15.879 --> 00:11:17.679
I'm so useless.

00:11:21.360 --> 00:11:22.720
So useless.

00:11:23.759 --> 00:11:26.799
This is us, the four brothers from Baofang.

00:11:26.799 --> 00:11:28.279
On our very first day.

00:11:28.399 --> 00:11:29.440
I'm talking.

00:11:29.440 --> 00:11:30.320
Then... then you speak.

00:11:30.320 --> 00:11:31.600
Go on, speak.

00:11:31.759 --> 00:11:32.840
I'm the big brother.

00:11:34.039 --> 00:11:35.200
I'm number one.

00:11:35.440 --> 00:11:36.320
I'm number two.

00:11:36.320 --> 00:11:37.279
You're number two.

00:11:38.159 --> 00:11:38.720
I'm number four.

00:11:38.720 --> 00:11:39.440
Weiguo is number three.

00:11:40.440 --> 00:11:41.480
Qiu'er is number four.

00:11:41.480 --> 00:11:42.799
I... I'm number one.

00:11:45.759 --> 00:11:46.480
Let's have a toast.

00:11:46.480 --> 00:11:46.960
Cheers.

00:12:10.480 --> 00:12:11.159
Manager Li.

00:12:11.759 --> 00:12:13.080
This is my resignation letter.

00:12:13.600 --> 00:12:14.679
An identical copy.

00:12:14.679 --> 00:12:15.960
I've already emailed it to you.

00:12:16.080 --> 00:12:16.960
What are you doing?

00:12:17.519 --> 00:12:18.960
The company hasn't said you have to leave.

00:12:20.639 --> 00:12:21.919
Given my current situation,

00:12:21.919 --> 00:12:23.519
the company will downsize me sooner or later.

00:12:23.879 --> 00:12:25.399
Rather than waiting to be laid off,

00:12:25.639 --> 00:12:27.120
I'd rather take the initiative.

00:12:27.440 --> 00:12:28.600
So little confidence?

00:12:29.279 --> 00:12:30.919
I'm almost thirty this year.

00:12:31.279 --> 00:12:32.639
The work I do at the company

00:12:32.639 --> 00:12:34.080
is all pretty dispensable.

00:12:34.720 --> 00:12:36.080
With this cost reduction and efficiency improvement,

00:12:36.080 --> 00:12:37.120
whether I'll be cut or not,

00:12:37.720 --> 00:12:39.080
I have a pretty good idea.

00:12:40.799 --> 00:12:41.559
Manager Li.

00:12:42.480 --> 00:12:44.120
Thank you for taking care of me all these years.

00:13:20.200 --> 00:13:22.279
Hello, Tech Support?

00:13:22.679 --> 00:13:23.600
This is Li Lianbao.

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:26.000
Uh, my computer won't turn on.

00:13:27.399 --> 00:13:29.720
What? It's locked?

00:13:30.639 --> 00:13:31.360
Why?

00:13:49.200 --> 00:13:50.519
Sorry, Manager Li.

00:13:50.519 --> 00:13:52.480
I'm just following the layoff list Kevin provided.

00:13:52.480 --> 00:13:53.639
That's what I'm executing.

00:13:53.879 --> 00:13:55.320
Please cooperate.

00:13:55.320 --> 00:13:56.679
Complete the procedures as soon as possible.

00:13:57.480 --> 00:13:59.759
Don't worry about the compensation part.

00:14:02.679 --> 00:14:03.919
You're deliberately screwing with me, right?

00:14:04.200 --> 00:14:04.960
Tom.

00:14:05.399 --> 00:14:08.320
I set a few criteria, for the sake of...

00:14:08.320 --> 00:14:09.200
What criteria?

00:14:09.200 --> 00:14:11.240
Which criteria could possibly put me on the chopping block?

00:14:12.519 --> 00:14:13.320
In terms of seniority,

00:14:13.759 --> 00:14:15.240
I've been at the company for twelve years.

00:14:15.480 --> 00:14:16.600
In terms of performance,

00:14:16.799 --> 00:14:19.000
my team was number one in the whole company last year.

00:14:19.320 --> 00:14:20.279
In terms of age,

00:14:21.000 --> 00:14:22.200
you're not any younger than me.

00:14:22.200 --> 00:14:23.799
I'm letting you go

00:14:23.799 --> 00:14:25.440
not because of age.

00:14:25.639 --> 00:14:26.320
Tom.

00:14:26.559 --> 00:14:29.000
For managers at your level,

00:14:29.000 --> 00:14:30.039
I'm actually quite lenient.

00:14:30.039 --> 00:14:31.080
Then on what grounds?

00:14:32.360 --> 00:14:33.159
Education.

00:14:34.799 --> 00:14:36.519
We are about to engage in closer business dealings

00:14:36.519 --> 00:14:38.679
with Rice.

00:14:39.440 --> 00:14:40.720
And as far as I know,

00:14:40.720 --> 00:14:42.600
you and Rice's president, Martin,

00:14:42.840 --> 00:14:44.919
seem to have some unpleasant history.

00:14:45.559 --> 00:14:47.279
Of course, saying this sounds ridiculous,

00:14:47.279 --> 00:14:48.559
but for me,

00:14:48.559 --> 00:14:50.399
it is indeed an unstable factor.

00:14:51.559 --> 00:14:52.399
Furthermore,

00:14:52.639 --> 00:14:55.039
your department also needs a new supervisor

00:14:55.039 --> 00:14:56.960
with broader vision and more potential for growth.

00:14:57.559 --> 00:14:59.639
You barely scraped into university back then,

00:14:59.840 --> 00:15:01.840
and are full of nothing but street-smart habits.

00:15:02.240 --> 00:15:03.960
This is not the company's future.

00:15:43.480 --> 00:15:44.440
Ma Weiguo.

00:15:45.240 --> 00:15:47.200
You really are going to ruin my whole life.

00:16:06.679 --> 00:16:07.480
Mr. Ma.

00:16:08.240 --> 00:16:10.120
Everything is ready.

00:16:10.240 --> 00:16:11.639
We can take the elder home now.

00:16:12.639 --> 00:16:13.879
Please sign here.

00:16:16.320 --> 00:16:17.159
In fifteen minutes,

00:16:17.159 --> 00:16:18.120
we'll depart.

00:16:39.480 --> 00:16:40.360
Your wife didn't come.

00:16:41.559 --> 00:16:43.519
She said she'd come to see off your aunt,

00:16:43.720 --> 00:16:44.879
but today at the shop,

00:16:44.879 --> 00:16:47.039
the fire department is coming for an inspection, someone has to stay.

00:16:51.440 --> 00:16:52.080
Director Dong.

00:16:53.000 --> 00:16:53.679
Uh...

00:16:54.240 --> 00:16:56.600
It wasn't convenient to talk at the funeral earlier.

00:16:56.600 --> 00:16:57.320
I wanted to ask,

00:16:57.320 --> 00:16:58.480
about that thing we discussed last time,

00:16:58.679 --> 00:17:00.039
how is it going?

00:17:02.200 --> 00:17:03.519
I have a meeting soon.

00:17:03.519 --> 00:17:05.400
Let's talk when we're both free.

00:17:08.799 --> 00:17:09.759
Actually, you don't need to...

00:17:09.759 --> 00:17:10.960
Just give me a brief rundown.

00:17:10.960 --> 00:17:11.839
Because my friend,

00:17:11.839 --> 00:17:12.880
he wants an update.

00:17:12.880 --> 00:17:14.200
So he can feel more at ease.

00:17:14.200 --> 00:17:15.359
A brief rundown?

00:17:15.680 --> 00:17:16.680
Recently, I

00:17:16.680 --> 00:17:19.000
do indeed plan to invest in a new F&B project.

00:17:19.720 --> 00:17:21.599
But I already have a target in mind.

00:17:21.720 --> 00:17:23.200
Your friend's conditions

00:17:23.200 --> 00:17:24.240
are still a bit lacking.

00:17:27.599 --> 00:17:29.039
You have a new target?

00:17:31.160 --> 00:17:32.279
Which one?

00:17:37.920 --> 00:17:38.720
Big brother

00:17:39.160 --> 00:17:39.920
Can we talk?

00:17:40.240 --> 00:17:40.839
Go ahead.

00:17:41.119 --> 00:17:43.319
I'm planning to invest in Penglexuan.

00:17:44.400 --> 00:17:45.880
Invest in Penglexuan.

00:17:46.720 --> 00:17:48.599
I happen to have a budget for it.

00:17:49.000 --> 00:17:49.680
I thought about it.

00:17:49.680 --> 00:17:52.000
Our Penglexuan is a century-old establishment.

00:17:52.119 --> 00:17:53.400
Compared to my other investments,

00:17:53.400 --> 00:17:54.599
it has more heritage.

00:17:54.599 --> 00:17:56.880
Penglexuan is indeed an old shop.

00:17:57.440 --> 00:17:58.119
So,

00:17:58.119 --> 00:17:59.559
we should cooperate well.

00:17:59.559 --> 00:18:01.319
Let's build Penglexuan up.

00:18:01.319 --> 00:18:02.480
No, Qianqian.

00:18:02.920 --> 00:18:04.720
You should invest in something else.

00:18:04.720 --> 00:18:05.559
You know your big brother

00:18:05.559 --> 00:18:07.119
isn't one for big ventures.

00:18:07.759 --> 00:18:10.000
Big brother, don't worry about that.

00:18:10.000 --> 00:18:10.880
On my side,

00:18:10.880 --> 00:18:12.519
I have a professional team.

00:18:12.640 --> 00:18:14.559
Once we have a proposal ready,

00:18:14.559 --> 00:18:16.279
we can discuss it in detail.

00:18:16.279 --> 00:18:16.839
Okay?

00:18:19.000 --> 00:18:19.799
Alright.

00:18:22.480 --> 00:18:23.279
Boss Dong.

00:18:25.160 --> 00:18:26.799
Are you here to pay respects to your aunt,

00:18:26.799 --> 00:18:28.079
or to talk business?

00:18:29.000 --> 00:18:31.079
You've been downsized by your company.

00:18:31.240 --> 00:18:32.480
Shouldn't you be job hunting,

00:18:32.480 --> 00:18:34.160
instead of criticizing me here?

00:18:34.319 --> 00:18:35.359
You were downsized?

00:18:36.240 --> 00:18:37.680
How did you get downsized?

00:18:37.759 --> 00:18:38.400
No.

00:18:38.480 --> 00:18:40.200
I resigned voluntarily.

00:18:40.200 --> 00:18:40.799
Right.

00:18:41.119 --> 00:18:43.119
I handed in my resignation

00:18:43.119 --> 00:18:44.680
before the official notice came.

00:18:45.240 --> 00:18:47.160
So, it sort of counts as voluntary.

00:18:48.079 --> 00:18:48.599
Wait.

00:18:48.599 --> 00:18:49.599
Don't you have a meeting?

00:18:49.599 --> 00:18:50.400
You should get going.

00:18:50.519 --> 00:18:51.440
So talkative.

00:18:53.079 --> 00:18:54.359
Seriously, Li Lianbao.

00:18:54.960 --> 00:18:56.480
If you really have nowhere to go,

00:18:56.480 --> 00:18:57.759
you could beg me.

00:18:58.160 --> 00:18:59.240
Maybe I'll soften up

00:18:59.240 --> 00:19:00.440
and actually find you a job.

00:19:00.440 --> 00:19:01.680
Take care. See you out.

00:19:04.240 --> 00:19:04.799
Fine.

00:19:05.240 --> 00:19:06.279
I'll head off then.

00:19:06.279 --> 00:19:06.799
I'm leaving.

00:19:06.799 --> 00:19:07.359
Take it easy.

00:19:07.359 --> 00:19:08.079
Bye, big brother.

00:19:08.359 --> 00:19:09.079
You take care too.

00:19:09.079 --> 00:19:09.559
Okay.

00:19:12.480 --> 00:19:14.079
Hey, what's going on with you?

00:19:16.680 --> 00:19:18.200
Don't worry, it's fine.

00:19:18.200 --> 00:19:19.480
Didn't I just say?

00:19:19.480 --> 00:19:20.599
Voluntary resignation.

00:19:23.559 --> 00:19:24.599
Big brother, big brother.

00:19:24.680 --> 00:19:27.200
Um, c-congratulations in advance, big brother.

00:19:27.200 --> 00:19:28.359
This Penglexuan...

00:19:28.359 --> 00:19:29.799
Someone's investing in it.

00:19:30.000 --> 00:19:31.000
What's this about?

00:19:31.000 --> 00:19:32.440
What's there to congratulate?

00:19:32.680 --> 00:19:33.680
It's a good thing!

00:19:34.000 --> 00:19:35.640
How about we hold the thank-you banquet

00:19:35.640 --> 00:19:37.279
right at Penglexuan?

00:19:38.200 --> 00:19:38.759
Sure.

00:19:39.079 --> 00:19:40.720
I'll help arrange things then.

00:19:41.039 --> 00:19:42.440
We're all family anyway.

00:19:42.839 --> 00:19:43.440
Thanks, big brother.

00:19:43.440 --> 00:19:43.920
Thank you, thank you, big brother.

00:19:43.920 --> 00:19:44.519
No problem, no problem.

00:19:44.519 --> 00:19:45.359
Well, we'll be going now.

00:19:45.359 --> 00:19:47.079
We have relatives at home for the wake,

00:19:47.079 --> 00:19:48.000
we need to attend to them.

00:19:48.000 --> 00:19:49.400
Alright, got it. Thanks for your trouble.

00:19:49.400 --> 00:19:51.000
You're the one working hard. Let's go.

00:19:51.319 --> 00:19:52.000
Leaving, big brother.

00:19:52.000 --> 00:19:52.319
Third brother, let's go.

00:19:52.319 --> 00:19:53.039
Take care, Xiaofang.

00:20:00.519 --> 00:20:01.960
Let's go to the old spot tomorrow night.

00:20:01.960 --> 00:20:02.960
No time.

00:20:03.319 --> 00:20:04.519
You have to go, even if you're busy.

00:20:04.920 --> 00:20:05.799
Why should I?

00:20:06.079 --> 00:20:07.319
Before Auntie passed,

00:20:07.680 --> 00:20:09.240
didn't she want the four of us to reconcile?

00:20:19.640 --> 00:20:20.279
Fine.

00:20:22.200 --> 00:20:23.039
Let's all go.

00:20:27.599 --> 00:20:28.160
Okay.

00:20:33.079 --> 00:20:33.640
Let's go.

00:21:14.279 --> 00:21:15.920
Why is everyone so quiet?

00:21:16.440 --> 00:21:17.920
Weren't we supposed to reconcile?

00:21:23.160 --> 00:21:24.640
This place is too loud.

00:21:24.640 --> 00:21:25.640
My head is pounding.

00:21:25.640 --> 00:21:26.799
I can't even breathe.

00:21:27.519 --> 00:21:28.920
Big brother, don't you remember?

00:21:28.920 --> 00:21:30.759
You used to bring us to places like this.

00:21:30.759 --> 00:21:33.160
You said, "He who hasn't been to the Great Wall is not a true man,"

00:21:33.160 --> 00:21:35.079
"and not loving to dance is a real shame."

00:21:42.200 --> 00:21:43.920
It's the same kind of place,

00:21:45.160 --> 00:21:46.799
but today's nightclubs

00:21:47.680 --> 00:21:49.839
are nothing like the old dance halls.

00:21:50.839 --> 00:21:51.920
Weiguo.

00:21:52.640 --> 00:21:54.039
Don't drink so much.

00:21:54.240 --> 00:21:55.160
Weiguo.

00:21:55.759 --> 00:21:56.720
Weiguo.

00:21:57.240 --> 00:21:58.920
Weiguo, I'm so glad you're back.

00:21:58.920 --> 00:22:00.359
I've been thinking about you.

00:22:00.359 --> 00:22:01.559
Why did you come back?

00:22:05.440 --> 00:22:07.319
Are people like him

00:22:07.319 --> 00:22:08.799
really popular abroad?

00:22:14.440 --> 00:22:16.240
I was the one who set up the meeting with Xue Mazi back then.

00:22:17.000 --> 00:22:18.400
The matter is already settled.

00:22:18.960 --> 00:22:20.039
Who told you to come?

00:22:20.480 --> 00:22:22.119
We were worried about you.

00:22:22.119 --> 00:22:23.079
Worried about me?

00:22:23.240 --> 00:22:25.920
You rushed out and started a fight without even knowing the facts.

00:22:25.920 --> 00:22:27.640
Otherwise, how could that fight have even happened?

00:22:28.440 --> 00:22:30.599
We shouldn't have gotten involved for your sake back then.

00:22:30.599 --> 00:22:32.359
We should've let Big Mazi finish you off.

00:22:32.799 --> 00:22:34.640
Then the whole thing with Liangzi wouldn't have happened.

00:22:35.599 --> 00:22:36.920
Shifting the blame, huh?

00:22:38.960 --> 00:22:40.519
Young Liangzi is already gone.

00:22:41.240 --> 00:22:42.400
I lost my guaranteed university admission.

00:22:42.400 --> 00:22:43.960
Big Brother spent two years in prison.

00:22:44.640 --> 00:22:46.319
None of these things have anything to do with you.

00:22:47.400 --> 00:22:48.599
Why did I go there?

00:22:48.759 --> 00:22:50.200
Who did I go there for?

00:22:50.200 --> 00:22:52.279
It was all because of you, Li Lianbao.

00:22:52.519 --> 00:22:53.640
Who was the one trying to play the hero?

00:22:53.680 --> 00:22:55.759
Who insisted on settling scores with those scumbags?

00:22:57.920 --> 00:22:59.119
I don't care what you say.

00:22:59.519 --> 00:23:00.799
My aunt is gone.

00:23:01.480 --> 00:23:03.839
Let's talk about what happened back then.

00:23:04.559 --> 00:23:05.319
Fine.

00:23:05.319 --> 00:23:05.960
Good.

00:23:06.440 --> 00:23:07.440
This is good.

00:23:07.640 --> 00:23:08.759
Should've done this long ago.

00:23:08.759 --> 00:23:09.400
Sit down.

00:23:11.920 --> 00:23:13.079
Before that,

00:23:14.119 --> 00:23:16.960
I want you to apologize to me.

00:23:18.799 --> 00:23:20.279
What do we have to apologize for?

00:23:20.279 --> 00:23:21.759
Back then, I told you guys,

00:23:22.000 --> 00:23:23.559
don't pick fights, don't pick fights.

00:23:24.480 --> 00:23:27.039
Big Brother, you think two years in prison makes you the victim?

00:23:27.559 --> 00:23:29.440
You think losing your spot at Beihang makes you the victim?

00:23:29.680 --> 00:23:31.160
Do you think I'm not a victim?

00:23:32.079 --> 00:23:34.160
Yes, you're all victims.

00:23:34.319 --> 00:23:35.200
Am I not one?

00:23:35.920 --> 00:23:36.839
I worked under the table.

00:23:36.839 --> 00:23:37.920
Lived in a warehouse.

00:23:38.359 --> 00:23:39.680
Listened to them curse at me.

00:23:40.279 --> 00:23:41.960
Watched them crack jokes I couldn't understand.

00:23:41.960 --> 00:23:42.920
And then they fired me.

00:23:44.200 --> 00:23:46.039
The year of the financial crisis, I went to Detroit.

00:23:46.279 --> 00:23:47.599
The city itself was bankrupt.

00:23:47.839 --> 00:23:49.440
No one wanted to go to that godforsaken place.

00:23:52.759 --> 00:23:54.079
Why did I go?

00:23:54.640 --> 00:23:55.759
Because there, one dollar

00:23:55.759 --> 00:23:57.200
could buy you a rundown house.

00:23:57.759 --> 00:23:59.079
I was twenty-four that year.

00:23:59.759 --> 00:24:01.599
Had to live day in, day out with a mob.

00:24:01.839 --> 00:24:03.640
They wanted to tear me apart every second.

00:24:04.079 --> 00:24:06.160
To vent their frustration and resentment after losing their jobs.

00:24:07.200 --> 00:24:08.799
Did I want to live like that?

00:24:09.039 --> 00:24:10.559
Did I deserve that life?

00:24:10.759 --> 00:24:11.519
No.

00:24:12.279 --> 00:24:14.640
Did you ever properly talk about this after you came back?

00:24:14.960 --> 00:24:16.640
You never spoke a single decent word.

00:24:16.640 --> 00:24:18.279
Were you ever nice to me?

00:24:19.079 --> 00:24:20.319
What did any of you ever show me?

00:24:20.319 --> 00:24:21.960
When Auntie was still alive,

00:24:23.559 --> 00:24:25.319
couldn't you have said something gentle?

00:24:26.240 --> 00:24:28.599
Couldn't you have just said something gentle?

00:24:28.599 --> 00:24:29.240
Well, did you ever say anything?

00:24:29.240 --> 00:24:30.240
Enough! This is endless! Will it ever end?

00:24:30.240 --> 00:24:30.960
Did you ever say anything?

00:24:30.960 --> 00:24:32.599
Auntie is gone now.

00:24:48.319 --> 00:24:49.079
Nice shot!

00:24:51.000 --> 00:24:52.519
Why aren't you kids in school?

00:24:54.440 --> 00:24:55.519
You lot, get up here!

00:24:57.480 --> 00:24:58.599
A-Auntie.

00:25:03.039 --> 00:25:04.519
In this life of mine,

00:25:05.440 --> 00:25:07.720
I wasn't a good mother.

00:25:08.039 --> 00:25:09.960
Because I was too easygoing.

00:25:10.799 --> 00:25:13.039
I wasn't a good daughter either.

00:25:13.400 --> 00:25:15.319
Because I was too playful.

00:25:16.000 --> 00:25:17.000
Got married,

00:25:17.119 --> 00:25:19.279
and all those trivial marital squabbles,

00:25:19.279 --> 00:25:20.440
the daily grind,

00:25:20.440 --> 00:25:22.039
I handled those poorly too.

00:25:22.319 --> 00:25:23.880
Because I had no patience.

00:25:24.720 --> 00:25:25.880
But isn't it strange,

00:25:25.960 --> 00:25:28.279
since you were little, the worry I poured into you kids,

00:25:28.279 --> 00:25:29.839
all that unnecessary fretting,

00:25:29.960 --> 00:25:31.359
I never complained.

00:25:31.519 --> 00:25:33.440
Never found it a bother.

00:25:33.599 --> 00:25:35.680
I never expected to get anything in return.

00:25:36.160 --> 00:25:38.960
Nor did I know if it was worth it or not.

00:26:04.160 --> 00:26:05.119
From now on,

00:26:05.240 --> 00:26:06.680
we sever all ties with him.

00:26:07.480 --> 00:26:08.640
We're brothers no more.

00:26:11.519 --> 00:26:12.559
I know

00:26:12.759 --> 00:26:16.240
there aren't that many second chances in this world.

00:26:16.880 --> 00:26:18.440
Whether it's Xu Liang,

00:26:18.640 --> 00:26:20.160
your uncle,

00:26:20.400 --> 00:26:22.440
or my own brothers and sisters,

00:26:22.680 --> 00:26:25.359
in the end, it all comes down to parting.

00:26:26.119 --> 00:26:28.640
Generation after generation of people,

00:26:28.839 --> 00:26:31.440
day after day of life,

00:26:31.920 --> 00:26:33.160
the joys and sorrows, meetings and partings,

00:26:33.160 --> 00:26:34.880
all depend on fate.

00:26:34.880 --> 00:26:36.200
You can't force it.

00:26:37.240 --> 00:26:39.000
But don't you forget,

00:26:39.359 --> 00:26:40.640
for men,

00:26:41.039 --> 00:26:43.359
the rarest quality is integrity.

00:26:43.440 --> 00:26:46.599
The cheapest thing is that bit of pride.

00:27:36.319 --> 00:27:37.240
You guys start eating.

00:27:37.240 --> 00:27:38.160
Eat up, all of you.

00:27:43.680 --> 00:27:44.200
Sister-in-law

00:27:44.279 --> 00:27:44.880
Sister-in-law

00:27:45.000 --> 00:27:45.599
Big brother

00:27:47.000 --> 00:27:48.720
Sister-in-law, sit, sit, sit.

00:27:49.079 --> 00:27:50.920
Big brother, I... I must toast you.

00:27:50.920 --> 00:27:52.440
You've truly worked hard all these years.

00:27:52.680 --> 00:27:53.200
It's my duty, my duty.

00:27:53.200 --> 00:27:53.880
To you.

00:27:54.279 --> 00:27:55.440
We're all family.

00:27:55.880 --> 00:27:56.839
And Auntie?

00:27:56.839 --> 00:27:58.440
In my heart, she was like a mother to me.

00:27:59.400 --> 00:28:00.640
And then, Xiaofang...

00:28:01.160 --> 00:28:03.240
Now that Auntie is gone...

00:28:04.720 --> 00:28:06.200
If you need anything in the future,

00:28:06.319 --> 00:28:09.319
you can tell me, tell your sister-in-law.

00:28:09.759 --> 00:28:10.079
Tell us.

00:28:10.079 --> 00:28:10.640
You should visit often.

00:28:10.640 --> 00:28:12.440
Come, you must, must visit often.

00:28:12.880 --> 00:28:14.240
Thank you, sister-in-law. Thank you, big brother.

00:28:14.240 --> 00:28:15.000
Thank you, big brother.

00:28:15.480 --> 00:28:16.119
Here, sister-in-law.

00:28:16.119 --> 00:28:17.240
Here, Fang.

00:28:21.559 --> 00:28:22.559
Sit, eat.

00:28:22.559 --> 00:28:24.039
Alright, you should eat something now.

00:28:24.039 --> 00:28:25.000
Let's tidy up.

00:28:28.599 --> 00:28:29.400
Everyone.

00:28:32.000 --> 00:28:33.720
I'm especially grateful to all my family,

00:28:33.720 --> 00:28:34.960
all the elders, for coming.

00:28:34.960 --> 00:28:36.319
Especially during this period,

00:28:36.319 --> 00:28:38.519
like Third Brother coming from afar,

00:28:38.960 --> 00:28:41.119
Second Brother, Qiu, have been a huge help.

00:28:41.119 --> 00:28:42.240
I've taken note of it all,

00:28:42.240 --> 00:28:42.960
and am deeply moved.

00:28:43.839 --> 00:28:44.880
Thank you all.

00:28:46.720 --> 00:28:47.880
As for Penglexuan,

00:28:47.880 --> 00:28:49.000
all these years,

00:28:49.000 --> 00:28:51.160
it's been a burden on my big brother to manage it.

00:28:51.160 --> 00:28:54.319
Actually, Fang and I have seen it,

00:28:54.720 --> 00:28:56.319
and it really doesn't sit right with us.

00:28:56.440 --> 00:28:57.680
It's what we should do.

00:28:57.680 --> 00:28:58.200
No, no, no.

00:28:58.200 --> 00:28:59.640
There's no "should" or "shouldn't" about it.

00:28:59.640 --> 00:29:00.920
There's a responsibility involved.

00:29:01.039 --> 00:29:01.759
Listen to me.

00:29:02.200 --> 00:29:03.400
Big brother, you listen to me first.

00:29:04.680 --> 00:29:06.680
So we've made a decision.

00:29:07.440 --> 00:29:08.680
Starting today,

00:29:09.000 --> 00:29:10.200
Fang and I

00:29:10.920 --> 00:29:12.519
want to help our big brother

00:29:12.519 --> 00:29:14.200
share the burden.

00:29:17.640 --> 00:29:18.759
Everyone knows

00:29:18.759 --> 00:29:21.119
that Penglexuan originally

00:29:21.519 --> 00:29:25.160
was also the inheritance of Xu Fang's grandfather.

00:29:25.839 --> 00:29:27.240
So however you look at it,

00:29:27.240 --> 00:29:29.720
we have the responsibility and duty

00:29:29.720 --> 00:29:32.599
to help our big brother share it, right?

00:29:44.000 --> 00:29:44.680
Fang.

00:29:45.319 --> 00:29:46.480
Is he drunk?

00:29:46.680 --> 00:29:47.240
A bit.

00:29:47.240 --> 00:29:48.000
No, no, that's not it.

00:29:48.000 --> 00:29:49.160
No, what are you sharing?

00:29:49.160 --> 00:29:50.359
Big brother, listen to me.

00:29:50.359 --> 00:29:53.880
Tang, today's occasion isn't suitable.

00:29:53.880 --> 00:29:54.960
If you really have something to say,

00:29:54.960 --> 00:29:56.720
talk to your big brother privately later.

00:29:56.720 --> 00:29:57.039
No, no, no.

00:29:57.039 --> 00:29:57.759
Sister-in-law is right.

00:29:57.759 --> 00:29:59.039
It's suitable, suitable, suitable.

00:29:59.039 --> 00:29:59.640
No, no.

00:29:59.640 --> 00:30:00.319
It's especially suitable.

00:30:00.319 --> 00:30:01.440
Sister-in-law, it's, it's suitable.

00:30:01.440 --> 00:30:02.079
Especially suitable.

00:30:02.079 --> 00:30:04.519
Sister-in-law, it has to be said today, sister-in-law.

00:30:04.519 --> 00:30:05.160
It has to be said today.

00:30:05.160 --> 00:30:06.119
Tang, Tang, Tang.

00:30:06.400 --> 00:30:07.359
Let me say something.

00:30:07.359 --> 00:30:08.599
Listen to your big brother, okay?

00:30:09.160 --> 00:30:10.240
Today,

00:30:10.440 --> 00:30:13.559
we're here for Auntie, right?

00:30:13.559 --> 00:30:15.119
We're here to thank everyone.

00:30:15.119 --> 00:30:17.279
Whatever it is, we can discuss it ourselves later.

00:30:17.279 --> 00:30:18.359
Okay? Fang, keep him in check.

00:30:18.359 --> 00:30:20.480
It's precisely because today is about my mom

00:30:20.640 --> 00:30:21.880
that it has to be said.

00:30:21.880 --> 00:30:23.319
Because this matter is related to my mom.

00:30:23.319 --> 00:30:24.279
Sister-in-law, it must be said.

00:30:24.279 --> 00:30:25.039
Why?

00:30:25.039 --> 00:30:26.680
Because everyone is here today.

00:30:26.880 --> 00:30:27.799
If everyone weren't here,

00:30:27.799 --> 00:30:28.519
and we agreed on something later,

00:30:28.519 --> 00:30:29.759
what if someone goes back on their word, right?

00:30:29.759 --> 00:30:31.200
I'm afraid someone might renege.

00:30:31.559 --> 00:30:32.920
Renege on what?

00:30:32.920 --> 00:30:33.880
Weasel out of a deal.

00:30:34.720 --> 00:30:36.160
I wondered why you insisted on holding

00:30:36.160 --> 00:30:37.519
this thank-you banquet at Penglexuan.

00:30:38.359 --> 00:30:40.759
I thought you just wanted to save some money.

00:30:41.000 --> 00:30:42.519
Turns out there's this act too.

00:30:42.960 --> 00:30:43.680
Alright then.

00:30:43.839 --> 00:30:45.160
Since everyone is here,

00:30:45.160 --> 00:30:47.039
say what's on your mind today.

00:30:47.279 --> 00:30:48.079
Big brother, big brother.

00:30:48.079 --> 00:30:49.240
It's actually very simple.

00:30:49.240 --> 00:30:50.640
What I mean to say is,

00:30:50.640 --> 00:30:52.559
that Penglexuan, for so many years,

00:30:52.559 --> 00:30:54.079
under my big brother's management...

00:30:54.319 --> 00:30:56.359
Big brother, the money you've...

00:30:57.839 --> 00:30:59.160
I think you've made enough.

00:30:59.519 --> 00:31:01.240
You should know when to stop.

00:31:02.680 --> 00:31:04.039
Even greed has its limits.

00:31:04.039 --> 00:31:05.200
What do you mean, "greedy"?

00:31:05.200 --> 00:31:06.039
Can you speak properly?

00:31:06.039 --> 00:31:07.000
What "what"? What's "what"?

00:31:07.000 --> 00:31:08.359
If it's not greed, what is it?

00:31:08.359 --> 00:31:09.519
Qiu, Qiu, Qiu.

00:31:09.519 --> 00:31:10.519
This has nothing to do with you.

00:31:10.519 --> 00:31:11.839
Don't speak, don't speak.

00:31:12.799 --> 00:31:13.640
Tang.

00:31:15.039 --> 00:31:17.119
A man whose heart is not content is like a snake trying to swallow an elephant.

00:31:18.000 --> 00:31:21.519
What the heck does Penglexuan have to do with you?

00:31:21.519 --> 00:31:23.839
No, big brother, you can't say that either.

00:31:27.279 --> 00:31:28.680
No, Xiaofang, why are you saying that too?

00:31:28.680 --> 00:31:29.480
What's wrong? What's wrong?

00:31:29.480 --> 00:31:30.359
Can't talk, is that it?

00:31:30.359 --> 00:31:31.680
Don't glare. Don't just glare like that.

00:31:31.680 --> 00:31:33.119
Come on, sit down. Sit down, sit down.

00:31:33.279 --> 00:31:35.480
Don't keep interrogating our Xu Fang.

00:31:35.480 --> 00:31:37.559
Emotional blackmail, moral blackmail, right?

00:31:37.799 --> 00:31:39.480
Bullying the honest one, aren't you?

00:31:40.000 --> 00:31:42.440
He was Xu Fang's grandfather too, wasn't he?

00:31:42.440 --> 00:31:44.359
How come it all goes to you alone?

00:31:44.920 --> 00:31:47.240
Just because our Xu Fang is a woman, right?

00:31:47.240 --> 00:31:47.960
Let me tell you.

00:31:47.960 --> 00:31:50.880
The inheritance law stipulates gender equality.

00:31:50.880 --> 00:31:51.680
Right on this point.

00:31:51.680 --> 00:31:52.200
Our Xu Fang...

00:31:52.200 --> 00:31:53.200
No, no, no, you sit.

00:31:53.759 --> 00:31:56.000
Xu Fang has the same rights as you.

00:31:56.000 --> 00:31:56.759
And I'll be honest with you.

00:31:56.759 --> 00:31:58.400
I've already hired a lawyer.

00:31:58.400 --> 00:31:59.480
If you keep making trouble like this,

00:31:59.480 --> 00:32:00.680
we'll see you in court.

00:32:00.680 --> 00:32:01.799
Don't give me that nonsense about

00:32:01.799 --> 00:32:03.400
inheritance law or no inheritance law.

00:32:03.640 --> 00:32:05.319
When Grandpa was still alive,

00:32:05.319 --> 00:32:06.400
in front of my mom,

00:32:06.599 --> 00:32:07.559
in front of my uncle,

00:32:07.680 --> 00:32:08.799
and in front of my aunt,

00:32:09.240 --> 00:32:11.039
he made a written agreement with me.

00:32:11.880 --> 00:32:14.519
Grandpa said whoever could inherit his craft

00:32:14.799 --> 00:32:16.480
would get the Penglexuan.

00:32:17.119 --> 00:32:18.759
It was stated clearly.

00:32:19.839 --> 00:32:20.920
And furthermore,

00:32:21.119 --> 00:32:24.160
it was my parents who took care of Grandma and Grandpa till the end.

00:32:25.119 --> 00:32:26.079
And as for you,

00:32:26.519 --> 00:32:28.079
Aunt only has this one daughter.

00:32:28.440 --> 00:32:29.359
You, her son-in-law,

00:32:29.359 --> 00:32:32.359
the financial hole you dug from years of business,

00:32:32.680 --> 00:32:33.799
it was us, my wife and I,

00:32:33.799 --> 00:32:35.839
who used the Penglexuan to fill it for you.

00:32:36.039 --> 00:32:37.599
Aunt remembered this kindness.

00:32:37.599 --> 00:32:39.519
That's why Aunt didn't claim the Penglexuan.

00:32:39.519 --> 00:32:42.119
If Aunt had said she wanted the Penglexuan,

00:32:42.119 --> 00:32:44.599
I would have handed it to her with both hands.

00:32:44.599 --> 00:32:45.759
And my mom said she didn't want it.

00:32:45.759 --> 00:32:46.599
There was that written agreement back then.

00:32:46.599 --> 00:32:47.880
I never heard of it.

00:32:47.880 --> 00:32:49.759
I never heard the old lady say that.

00:32:49.759 --> 00:32:50.319
I never heard of it.

00:32:50.319 --> 00:32:51.720
How could you not have heard of it?

00:32:51.960 --> 00:32:53.400
Are you drunk or something?

00:32:53.400 --> 00:32:54.519
No, do you have any proof?

00:32:54.519 --> 00:32:55.519
Do you have any proof?

00:32:55.519 --> 00:32:57.680
No, there was a written agreement back then!

00:32:57.680 --> 00:32:58.400
Have you seen it?

00:32:58.400 --> 00:32:59.759
Have you seen the agreement?

00:32:59.759 --> 00:33:00.440
I haven't seen it.

00:33:00.440 --> 00:33:00.839
Stop saying that.

00:33:00.839 --> 00:33:01.440
You've seen it, you produce it.

00:33:01.440 --> 00:33:01.880
Brother, produce it.

00:33:01.880 --> 00:33:03.200
No, Xiao Tang, let me tell you.

00:33:03.680 --> 00:33:06.039
The Penglexuan has been renovated so many times.

00:33:06.039 --> 00:33:07.599
The back rooms have been redone over and over.

00:33:07.599 --> 00:33:08.759
Done several times.

00:33:08.960 --> 00:33:10.319
We've moved how many times?

00:33:10.319 --> 00:33:11.599
I really can't find that thing anymore.

00:33:11.599 --> 00:33:12.440
Then it doesn't exist.

00:33:12.440 --> 00:33:14.079
If you can't produce it, it doesn't exist.

00:33:14.160 --> 00:33:15.880
He can't produce it, so it doesn't exist, right?

00:33:15.880 --> 00:33:17.039
Xiao Tang, Xiao Tang.

00:33:17.160 --> 00:33:18.720
You have to speak with a conscience.

00:33:18.720 --> 00:33:20.359
You said it yourself.

00:33:20.359 --> 00:33:22.000
We're all family.

00:33:22.000 --> 00:33:23.000
We trust each other.

00:33:23.000 --> 00:33:24.599
So we don't need to rewrite it, right?

00:33:24.599 --> 00:33:26.079
How can you turn around and deny it?

00:33:26.079 --> 00:33:29.039
Besides, the Penglexuan is a matter between the siblings.

00:33:29.039 --> 00:33:31.319
To put it bluntly, we're both outsiders.

00:33:31.319 --> 00:33:33.000
You shouldn't be saying this here.

00:33:33.000 --> 00:33:33.720
It's not appropriate.

00:33:33.720 --> 00:33:35.839
Sister-in-law, you shouldn't be the one saying that.

00:33:35.839 --> 00:33:36.599
Let me tell you.

00:33:36.599 --> 00:33:38.039
You can't talk like that.

00:33:38.039 --> 00:33:39.160
Don't touch. Don't point.

00:33:39.160 --> 00:33:39.880
What? What?

00:33:39.880 --> 00:33:40.640
Why can't I point?

00:33:40.640 --> 00:33:41.319
What do you mean?

00:33:41.319 --> 00:33:42.440
Spouting nonsense here.

00:33:42.440 --> 00:33:43.680
Don't act drunk here.

00:33:43.680 --> 00:33:45.200
Sorry, sorry.

00:33:45.200 --> 00:33:47.160
She makes it sound like we planned this all along,

00:33:47.160 --> 00:33:48.240
to swindle their family.

00:33:48.240 --> 00:33:49.680
Stop making a scene. You've gone too far.

00:33:49.680 --> 00:33:51.000
You're wronging a good person.

00:33:51.359 --> 00:33:52.559
You're wronging me.

00:33:52.559 --> 00:33:53.720
No, how are you talking to your sister-in-law?

00:33:53.720 --> 00:33:54.680
What? What?

00:33:54.680 --> 00:33:55.640
Why can't I talk to my sister-in-law like this?

00:33:55.640 --> 00:33:56.359
He's had a bit too much to drink.

00:33:56.359 --> 00:33:57.759
Sorry, had too much, had too much.

00:33:57.759 --> 00:33:58.200
It's okay.

00:33:58.200 --> 00:33:59.039
I'm not talking to him anymore.

00:33:59.039 --> 00:34:00.319
He said it. He said it. My word is useless.

00:34:00.319 --> 00:34:01.480
Had too much, had too much.

00:34:01.480 --> 00:34:02.359
He said it.

00:34:02.599 --> 00:34:03.319
He said it, okay?

00:34:03.319 --> 00:34:04.079
Sorry.

00:34:04.079 --> 00:34:05.240
If I'm no use,

00:34:05.240 --> 00:34:06.319
then my mom will be of use.

00:34:06.319 --> 00:34:07.680
Come on, come on.

00:34:07.680 --> 00:34:08.760
You tell my mom.

00:34:08.760 --> 00:34:09.800
You tell my mom.

00:34:10.159 --> 00:34:11.199
Xiao Tang, this is not right.

00:34:11.199 --> 00:34:12.800
Don't move. Talk to my mom.

00:34:15.000 --> 00:34:16.280
No, are you crazy?

00:34:17.199 --> 00:34:18.599
What are you doing with Aunt's portrait?

00:34:28.079 --> 00:34:30.280
What are you trying to do?

00:34:31.079 --> 00:34:32.840
Wang Chunsheng, you...

00:34:32.840 --> 00:34:34.880
My mom even said you were a good person.

00:34:34.880 --> 00:34:37.119
Is this how you treat us well?

00:34:37.119 --> 00:34:39.159
Xiao Tang, what are you... what are you doing?

00:34:39.159 --> 00:34:40.719
Aren't you just causing trouble?

00:34:40.719 --> 00:34:41.880
It's okay, it's okay, it's okay.

00:34:41.880 --> 00:34:42.920
He's drunk.

00:34:46.360 --> 00:34:47.239
Tang Zhixin!

00:34:47.239 --> 00:34:48.719
Go ahead, smash another one, I dare you.

00:34:49.320 --> 00:34:50.119
He's bleeding.

00:34:50.119 --> 00:34:50.880
He's bleeding!

00:34:50.880 --> 00:34:52.360
Quick, call the police!

00:34:52.360 --> 00:34:53.159
Call the police!

00:34:53.159 --> 00:34:54.559
Go ahead, call them! What are you gonna do?

00:34:55.880 --> 00:34:57.280
Too impulsive.

00:34:57.280 --> 00:34:58.480
Call the police!

00:34:58.480 --> 00:35:00.039
So much blood. Does it hurt?

00:35:00.039 --> 00:35:00.960
It hurts.

00:35:03.119 --> 00:35:04.519
Hurry, call the police!

00:35:05.000 --> 00:35:06.360
Who's calling the police?

00:35:06.480 --> 00:35:07.480
Who's calling the police?

00:35:07.480 --> 00:35:08.400
Let me see.

00:35:08.840 --> 00:35:10.480
No, Brother, how could you hit someone?

00:35:10.480 --> 00:35:11.639
He was trying to kill me!

00:35:11.639 --> 00:35:13.400
No matter what, you can't hit someone!

00:35:13.400 --> 00:35:15.079
Call the police quickly!

00:35:16.079 --> 00:35:16.960
Brother...

00:35:25.119 --> 00:35:26.559
You two come with us

00:35:26.559 --> 00:35:27.199
Let's go

00:35:28.639 --> 00:35:29.480
Officer

00:35:29.480 --> 00:35:31.039
I really didn't fight back

00:35:31.039 --> 00:35:31.760
I didn't hit back even once

00:35:31.760 --> 00:35:32.840
Get in the car, don't talk

00:35:33.079 --> 00:35:34.199
I... I'm not getting in this car

00:35:34.199 --> 00:35:34.760
Get in

00:35:34.760 --> 00:35:35.159
I won't

00:35:35.159 --> 00:35:35.840
Get in, get in

00:35:35.840 --> 00:35:38.000
Hurry up, get in the car

00:35:47.519 --> 00:35:48.280
Lao Er

00:35:49.719 --> 00:35:50.519
Don't worry

00:36:10.039 --> 00:36:10.639
Sister-in-law

00:36:10.639 --> 00:36:11.320
Lao Er

00:36:14.079 --> 00:36:14.599
Uncle

00:36:15.599 --> 00:36:16.320
Feifei

00:36:16.760 --> 00:36:18.639
Go back to your room and study

00:36:18.639 --> 00:36:19.920
I'll discuss this with your mom

00:36:21.440 --> 00:36:22.920
It's fine, go on

00:36:23.920 --> 00:36:26.079
I was thinking I could help figure something out

00:36:26.079 --> 00:36:27.760
I can help come up with ideas too

00:36:27.760 --> 00:36:28.880
Be good, go

00:36:37.519 --> 00:36:38.199
Lao Er

00:36:38.760 --> 00:36:40.719
Look at your big brother's age

00:36:40.719 --> 00:36:42.639
How can he still be so reckless?

00:36:42.639 --> 00:36:44.280
Sister-in-law, you don't need to worry

00:36:44.840 --> 00:36:46.599
My friend introduced a lawyer to me

00:36:47.679 --> 00:36:49.119
He is very skilled

00:36:49.119 --> 00:36:50.880
He's willing to take this case too

00:36:53.000 --> 00:36:54.880
If you found him, he must be good

00:36:56.440 --> 00:36:58.400
The legal fees... I'll transfer to you

00:36:58.519 --> 00:36:59.079
No need

00:36:59.079 --> 00:37:00.719
Don't worry about the money

00:37:00.719 --> 00:37:01.880
It's just the cost of a couple of meals

00:37:05.800 --> 00:37:07.679
Is it really serious this time?

00:37:08.119 --> 00:37:09.760
Will he be locked up for three to five years?

00:37:11.199 --> 00:37:12.280
Rest assured

00:37:12.280 --> 00:37:13.480
I'll go contact him right now

00:37:13.480 --> 00:37:15.320
Then... then you keep an eye on things

00:37:16.039 --> 00:37:17.079
Take care

00:37:36.119 --> 00:37:37.320
Our branch

00:37:37.320 --> 00:37:39.199
in Wangping Village, Mentougou

00:37:39.199 --> 00:37:40.679
has opened a new outlet

00:37:40.800 --> 00:37:42.239
We need to send a senior employee

00:37:42.239 --> 00:37:43.519
to support them for a while

00:37:44.119 --> 00:37:46.440
The candidate has already been reported

00:37:47.360 --> 00:37:49.159
That's all for today, meeting adjourned

00:37:56.800 --> 00:37:57.960
Wangping Village

00:38:05.119 --> 00:38:05.800
Tong

00:38:06.559 --> 00:38:07.320
You stay

00:38:13.440 --> 00:38:16.159
The new outlet in Wangping Village, Mentougou is opening

00:38:16.639 --> 00:38:17.639
They are short-handed

00:38:17.920 --> 00:38:19.280
You go support them for a few months

00:38:21.360 --> 00:38:22.119
Manager Liu

00:38:22.119 --> 00:38:23.639
Is it because of Mr. Qiu?

00:38:23.639 --> 00:38:24.840
Don't make wild connections

00:38:24.960 --> 00:38:26.440
It has nothing to do with Mr. Qiu

00:38:26.840 --> 00:38:28.440
Today let's talk about your issues

00:38:30.159 --> 00:38:31.159
Look at this yourself

00:38:31.800 --> 00:38:33.039
The performance indicators for the last six months

00:38:33.039 --> 00:38:34.320
you haven't properly completed any

00:38:34.519 --> 00:38:36.000
And your attendance record

00:38:36.199 --> 00:38:37.760
In a month, you're late for half of it

00:38:37.760 --> 00:38:39.000
The other half, you leave early

00:38:39.000 --> 00:38:40.039
You don't even file for leave

00:38:40.199 --> 00:38:41.159
You just leave it like that

00:38:41.280 --> 00:38:43.639
Yes, I really have some family matters recently

00:38:43.639 --> 00:38:45.599
Daily reports, monthly reports, quarterly reports, annual reports

00:38:45.599 --> 00:38:47.599
Look at what you wrote yourself

00:38:48.599 --> 00:38:49.880
Don't be angry

00:38:50.639 --> 00:38:52.239
It... it is my fault

00:38:52.239 --> 00:38:53.800
It really is my fault

00:38:55.719 --> 00:38:58.239
Even Little Zhou, who's only been here a few years, is better than you

00:38:58.320 --> 00:38:59.480
If you don't go, who will?

00:38:59.599 --> 00:39:00.440
Darn it

00:39:02.519 --> 00:39:03.440
No, no, no

00:39:05.159 --> 00:39:06.079
I recently...

00:39:06.079 --> 00:39:08.920
really have a deposit waiting to come in

00:39:09.800 --> 00:39:10.760
Just you?

00:39:12.519 --> 00:39:13.840
If you can really bring it in

00:39:14.079 --> 00:39:15.920
I'll transfer you back immediately

00:39:17.239 --> 00:39:18.320
Go this afternoon

00:39:42.920 --> 00:39:44.679
Who left their cup in the conference room?

00:39:44.679 --> 00:39:46.039
Come back and get it

00:39:49.880 --> 00:39:50.920
What is this?

00:39:55.639 --> 00:39:56.280
Lawyer Zhang

00:39:56.519 --> 00:39:58.199
That's the situation

00:39:58.320 --> 00:40:00.440
The rest is entirely up to your arrangement

00:40:00.800 --> 00:40:02.519
Just... the sooner the better

00:40:04.679 --> 00:40:05.840
I have a rough idea

00:40:07.519 --> 00:40:08.239
Lawyer Zhang

00:40:08.559 --> 00:40:11.119
What do you think are the chances?

00:40:13.719 --> 00:40:14.639
It's hard to say

00:40:15.440 --> 00:40:17.400
Civil compensation is definitely unavoidable

00:40:18.440 --> 00:40:20.159
As for the other party's litigation demands

00:40:20.159 --> 00:40:21.920
I have to judge based on the actual situation

00:40:23.599 --> 00:40:24.480
Excuse me

00:40:24.840 --> 00:40:26.440
Let's stop here for today

00:40:26.920 --> 00:40:27.920
The subsequent procedures

00:40:27.920 --> 00:40:29.039
I'll find a time to go over them with you

00:40:30.039 --> 00:40:30.960
No way

00:40:32.039 --> 00:40:33.400
He won't really be sentenced, will he?

00:40:33.400 --> 00:40:34.199
He used to...

00:40:34.199 --> 00:40:34.960
Sister-in-law

00:40:35.400 --> 00:40:37.800
This court isn't owned by Tang Zhixin's family

00:40:37.800 --> 00:40:39.159
It's not like whatever he says goes

00:40:39.760 --> 00:40:40.840
Let's listen to the lawyer

00:40:44.599 --> 00:40:46.159
Lawyer Zhang, someone is looking for you

00:40:46.159 --> 00:40:47.000
Do they have an appointment?

00:40:48.079 --> 00:40:49.719
It's Lawyer Liu from Daheng

00:40:53.559 --> 00:40:56.320
Um, Lawyer Zhang, thank you

00:40:56.519 --> 00:40:57.960
No problem, it's my duty

00:40:58.679 --> 00:41:00.599
Old Zhang, I'll treat you to a meal later

00:41:01.000 --> 00:41:01.519
Okay

00:41:02.519 --> 00:41:03.679
I won't see you out then

00:41:03.679 --> 00:41:04.320
Please, stay

00:41:04.320 --> 00:41:04.599
Take care, take care

00:41:04.599 --> 00:41:04.960
Weiguo

00:41:04.960 --> 00:41:05.960
Leaving so soon?

00:41:08.840 --> 00:41:10.079
Why are you here too?

00:41:10.639 --> 00:41:13.840
Big Zhang, I came uninvited

00:41:13.840 --> 00:41:16.239
Senior Brother, I'm honored by your visit

00:41:17.280 --> 00:41:18.400
Let me introduce a friend

00:41:18.400 --> 00:41:21.679
This is Mr. Martin from the US headquarters

00:41:21.880 --> 00:41:23.159
Mr. Martin, nice to meet you

00:41:23.159 --> 00:41:23.920
If there's anything

00:41:23.920 --> 00:41:25.000
let's go inside and talk

00:41:25.400 --> 00:41:26.239
Together, in a bit

00:41:26.360 --> 00:41:26.800
Okay

00:41:26.800 --> 00:41:27.880
Come, come, inside, inside

00:41:28.159 --> 00:41:28.719
Senior Brother

00:41:28.719 --> 00:41:30.280
I found a large conference room for you

00:41:31.119 --> 00:41:32.280
Why is he here?

00:41:33.000 --> 00:41:34.199
How would I know?

00:41:34.639 --> 00:41:35.440
Let's go have a look first